title: Back to the Start
info:
I wrote Back to the Start for my "Abitur" celebration in 2005, picked up the song in 2007 and recorded it at "music and friends" to release it at the demoscene party TUM07. 

---
Back to the Start (lyrics and music: palindrome, arrangement: Jan Obergfell)
---
Placed 7th at tUM 07 "streamed music" division.
